title: Person of Interest S2E14 - Ending
author: Morgs K
comment: I dunno man there’s just something about Reese playing basketball in that suit that makes me laugh

It's adorable how Reese seemed a little hurt that Finch broke his "gift." lol

Also, you'd think Pierce Logan would be just grateful enough to the POI team for Root to recruit him in the current fight against Samaritan.
I miss this show. Great cast,plot lines are very possible in today’s America.

just rewatching the series again...it's uncanny how many of the side character, some one off's like Logan here, and some like Agent Stone, wound up in House of Cards and other acclaimed series. Show will never get old
description: Classic ending with the exact amount of dark humour
